OL,6,FA drunk driver who downed seven pints
OL,7,Fof lager and five shots of tequila
OL,8,Fleft another motorist with life-
OL,9,Fchanging injuries.
OL,11,FJoseph Dearden, 27, escaped his
OL,12,Fsmashed van and tried to flee the
OL,13,Fscene but was detained by residents
OL,14,Fwho witnessed the crash.
OL,16,FHe was so drunk when police arrested
OL,17,Fhim he was captured on body-cam
OL,18,Ffootage slurring to the cops: "All I
OL,19,Fhave to do is play the mental health
OL,20,Fcard."
