OL,6,FNow the ''callous and cowardly'
OL,7,Fdriver, from Bolton, has been jailed
OL,8,Ffollowing the crash which left a
OL,9,Fnumber of smashed up cars and debris
OL,10,Fstrewn all over a residential street.
OL,12,FThe incident began when Dearden drove
OL,13,Fin his company-owned Renault Trafic
OL,14,Fvan to Nook & Cranny pub on Darwen
OL,15,FRoad in the Bromley Cross area of
OL,16,FBolton at 6.33pm on Friday, August 13,
OL,17,F2021.
