OL,6,FWhat followed was a three-hour and 40
OL,7,Fminute bender in which the subsequent
OL,8,Fpolice investigation found he downed
OL,9,Fseven pints of lager and five shots of
OL,10,Ftequila.
OL,12,FCCTV showed Dearden staggering out of
OL,13,Fthe pub, towards the front door and
OL,14,F'acting in a drunken and erratic
OL,15,Fmanner', according to police.
OL,17,FHe was captured swaying and
OL,18,F'staggering backwards and forwards'
OL,19,Fclearly unsteady on his feet.
