OL,3,CResidents detained drunk van driver
OL,4,Cafter horror crash
OL,6,FHe was so drunk he grabbed at items
OL,7,Fround him to maintain upright. Despite
OL,8,Fhis condition, he got behind the wheel
OL,9,Fof his van.
OL,11,FHe drove out of the pub away from the
OL,12,Fpub along Darwen Road where, at speed
OL,13,Fand on the wrong side of the road, he
OL,14,Fcollided with parked vehicles and
OL,15,Fsmashed head-on into another and then
OL,16,Fcareered into a Range Rover.
OL,18,FThe head-on smash left the 25-year-old
OL,19,Fdriver of the car with life-changing
OL,20,Finjuries, police have revealed.
