OL,3,CResidents detained drunk van driver
OL,4,Cafter horror crash
OL,6,FOn impact, Dearden hit his head on the
OL,7,Fwindscreen of his van, causing a head
OL,8,Finjury. The police mugshot taken
OL,9,Fafterwards reveals the damage caused
OL,10,Fto his face.
OL,12,FWitnesses reported that Dearden became
OL,13,Fincreasingly aggressive and then tried
OL,14,Fto flee the scene.
OL,16,FDearden, of Hathaway Drive in Bolton,
OL,17,Fwas jailed for two-and-a-half years
OL,18,Fafter he pleaded guilty to causing
OL,19,Fserious injury by dangerous driving
OL,20,Fand driving whilst unfit through drink.
