OL,6,FAfter the hearing, Sergeant Antony
OL,7,FHannon, of GMP's Road Policing Unit
OL,8,Fbased in Eccles, said: "Firstly, I
OL,9,Fmust thank the victim for being strong
OL,10,Fthroughout the entire investigation
OL,11,Falongside multiple surgeries."
OL,13,F"I must also thank their family for
OL,14,Fsupporting them through it."
OL,16,F"Dearden's reckless actions that night
OL,17,Fleft the victim, a 25-year-old man,
OL,18,Fwith serious life-changing injuries.
OL,19,FHis behaviour on the night in trying
OL,20,Fto flee the scene after consuming
OL,21,Falcohol all night was cowardly.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
