OL,6,F"Dearden has never shown any remorse
OL,7,For apologised to the victim and his
OL,8,Fdisregard for the victim and his
OL,9,Factions is callous.
OL,11,F"I must thank the witnesses who
OL,12,Fdetained Dearden at the scene and
OL,13,Fassisted with the extensive
OL,14,Finvestigation that has been carried
OL,15,Fout.
OL,17,F"I hope today's sentencing will give
OL,18,Fsome confidence to the family going
OL,19,Fforward."
